# No environment variables are required to build or run this site.
#
# The values below are PUBLIC identifiers (safe to commit) used by
# scripts/fetch-content.mjs, overridable only for testing against a
# different project/dataset:
#
# SANITY_PROJECT_ID="79vh6zyc"
# SANITY_DATASET="production"
#
# SANITY_API_WRITE_TOKEN (in .env.local, NEVER committed) is used only by
# content-seeding scripts — it is a Node-side secret and must never get a
# VITE_ prefix (VITE_* vars are bundled into the public client build).
